{"about_the_game":"<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Painter Simulator: paint the whole world!</h2></strong><br><br><strong>PAINTER SIMULATOR</strong> is a new-generation game in which the emphasis is placed on the player's imagination and perceptiveness. Create the world in the colors you want to see with a<strong> brush</strong>. The use of individual colors will make certain objects, vehicles or characters start to move, thus, going through the next stages of the game, you will discover the story and become its participant.<br><br>It will be up to you how the game unfolds. Become a leader and decide where the action of the scenario maps will take.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052780/extras/be-a-hero.gif?t=1730815124\" /><br><br><strong>Be an artist</strong> - Unlock game modes where you can decide for yourself whether the leaves will be blue or the grass will be purple. Be creative and create your own image. The <strong>color palette</strong> is waiting for the first play.<br><br><strong>Paint</strong> - Make friends with <strong>colors</strong>, give them a new meaning. Fill the scene with color in many ways. Don't waste time on a regular crayon, try rain from spilled paint. <strong>Paint </strong>the walls with a brush and you will see what the effect will be.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052780/extras/explore.gif?t=1730815124\" /><br><br><strong>Scenarios and Adventures</strong> - Bring painted elements to life, giving them a new meaning. Be a spectator and watch what happens next.<br>Rob the bank and don't get caught. Fasten your seat belt and win the race.<br>Make a beautiful lady fall in love with you or experience a safari adventure. Here you have everything at your fingertips.<br><br><strong>Upgrade your skills</strong> - Don't give up on a loss just because something went wrong. You decide which painting mode you 